## 9. SQL 语句：INSERT

### 基础语法

```sql
-- 值插入
INSERT INTO klines VALUES ('BTCUSDT', 1700000001, 42500.0);

-- 多行
INSERT INTO klines VALUES
    ('BTCUSDT', 1700000001, 42500.0),
    ('ETHUSDT', 1700000001, 2300.0);

-- FROM SELECT
INSERT INTO klines SELECT * FROM new_klines;

-- 指定列
INSERT INTO klines (symbol, ts, close) VALUES ('BTCUSDT', 1700000001, 42500.0);
```

### BY POSITION vs BY NAME

```sql
-- BY POSITION（默认）：按列声明顺序映射
INSERT INTO klines BY POSITION VALUES ('BTCUSDT', 1700000001, 42500.0);

-- BY NAME：按列名匹配（列顺序不同时更安全）
INSERT INTO klines BY NAME (SELECT 42500.0 AS close, 'BTCUSDT' AS symbol, 1700000001 AS ts);
```

### ON CONFLICT（Upsert，量化场景常用）

```sql
-- 冲突时忽略（去重插入）
INSERT INTO klines VALUES ('BTCUSDT', 1700000001, 42500.0)
ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;

-- 简写
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO klines VALUES ('BTCUSDT', 1700000001, 42500.0);

-- 冲突时更新（标准 upsert）
-- EXCLUDED 虚拟表代表"要插入但冲突了的那一行"
INSERT INTO klines (symbol, ts, close, volume)
VALUES ('BTCUSDT', 1700000001, 42600.0, 2000.0)
ON CONFLICT (symbol, ts) DO UPDATE SET
    close = EXCLUDED.close,
    volume = EXCLUDED.volume;

-- 简写（更新所有列）
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO klines VALUES ('BTCUSDT', 1700000001, 42600.0, 2000.0);

-- 带条件的 upsert（仅当新值更大时更新）
INSERT INTO klines VALUES ('BTCUSDT', 1700000001, 42600.0, 2000.0)
ON CONFLICT (symbol, ts) DO UPDATE SET
    close = EXCLUDED.close
WHERE EXCLUDED.close > klines.close;
```

### RETURNING（获取插入结果）

```sql
-- 返回插入的行（可用于获取自增 ID）
INSERT INTO orders (symbol, qty) VALUES ('BTCUSDT', 10)
RETURNING *;

INSERT INTO orders (symbol, qty) VALUES ('BTCUSDT', 10)
RETURNING order_id, created_at;
```

