## 10. SQL 语句：UPDATE

### 基础语法

```sql
-- 更新满足条件的行
UPDATE klines SET close = 0.0 WHERE close IS NULL;

-- 更新多列
UPDATE klines SET close = 42600.0, volume = 2000.0
WHERE symbol = 'BTCUSDT' AND ts = 1700000001;
```

### UPDATE FROM（用另一张表的值更新）

量化场景常用：把新数据表的值同步到主表：

```sql
-- FROM 另一张表
UPDATE klines
SET close = new_data.close,
    volume = new_data.volume
FROM new_data
WHERE klines.symbol = new_data.symbol
  AND klines.ts = new_data.ts;

-- FROM 子查询
UPDATE klines
SET close = (
    SELECT nd.close
    FROM new_data nd
    WHERE klines.symbol = nd.symbol
      AND klines.ts = nd.ts
);
```

### UPDATE FROM 同一张表（自引用）

```sql
-- 同表更新需要用别名区分
UPDATE klines AS k
SET close = (
    SELECT adjusted.close * 1.01
    FROM klines AS adjusted
    WHERE k.symbol = adjusted.symbol
      AND adjusted.ts = k.ts - 1
);
```

### UPDATE + JOIN 模式

```sql
-- 用 JOIN 更新：把法国城市收入增加 100
UPDATE city
SET revenue = revenue + 100
FROM country
WHERE city.country_code = country.code
  AND country.name = 'France';
```

